# The chat surface: lists, help sections, detail cards — real dev data.
Output chat.gif
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 900
Set Padding 12
Type "../../../pito-tui"
Enter
Sleep 4s
Enter
Sleep 2s
Type "ls games"
Enter
Sleep 5s
Screenshot games.png
Type "/help"
Enter
Sleep 5s
Screenshot help.png
Type "show vid #28"
Enter
Sleep 5s
Screenshot detail.png
Ctrl+C
